{"type": "article", "id": 26356, "title": "墙上收纳盒", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-04T07:19:12Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 79, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703121402Ms5PDSenJx1pvKIC.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">来自美国俄勒冈州波特兰的品牌 <a href=\"http://grovemade.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Grovemade</a> 以手工制作的木制科技产品外壳以及桌上配件而出名。对于打算利用墙面的收纳控来说，他们新推出的 Catch-All 可以满足你的需求。内嵌的羊毛防止物品产生划痕，盒子底部还安装了三个黄铜挂钩，是挂钥匙的完美选择。它售价为 149 美元，可以通过<a href=\"http://grovemade.com/product/walnut-catch-all/?initial=203\">链接</a>购买。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121359xwiKqSQnMsYdjR7U.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px; height: 250px; width: 375px; left: 661px; top: 803px;\" class=\"dragged\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121359vdOKfClQ6tDrex2k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121400rygzlt3FKqTjOA6P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121401PTVpKJhDQydcg5FC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68888889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}